<section id="gls_id">
  <title>id</title>

  <para>Identifier - a character string used to identify a <olink
      targetdoc="../../elements/glossary/glossentry.xml" targetptr="glossentry"
        ><code>&lt;glossEntry></code></olink> or <olink
      targetdoc="../../elements/glossary/translation.xml" targetptr="translation"
        ><code>&lt;translation></code></olink> element.</para>

  <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis> NMTOKEN</para>

  <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> undefined</para>

  <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis><olink targetdoc="../../elements/glossary/glossentry.xml" targetptr="glossentry"><code>&lt;glossEntry></code></olink> and <olink targetdoc="../../elements/glossary/translation.xml" targetptr="translation"><code>&lt;translation></code></olink></para>
<itemizedlist>
  <title>Constraints</title>
  <listitem>
    <para>The values of <link linkend="gls_id"><code>id</code></link> attributes <glossterm>must</glossterm> be unique among all <olink targetdoc="../../elements/glossary/glossentry.xml" targetptr="glossentry"><code>&lt;glossEntry></code></olink> 
    and <olink targetdoc="../../elements/glossary/translation.xml" targetptr="translation"><code>&lt;translation></code></olink> elements within the given enclosing 
      <olink targetdoc="../../elements/glossary/glossary.xml" targetptr="glossary"><code>&lt;glossary></code></olink> element.
    </para>
  </listitem>
</itemizedlist>  


</section>
